Package com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models.Booking
@Entity public class Booking extends Object
Represents a booking entity in the system. Contains details about the booking date, associated passenger, flight, seat, and user.
